          "merged_at": "2025-10-28T20:36:09Z"
        },
        "body": "Title: Fix: Enhance ChatHeader Error Handling and Loading States\r\n\r\nDescription:\r\n## Problem\r\nThe ChatHeader component lacked proper error handling and loading states, which could lead to:\r\n- Runtime errors when selectedUser data is not immediately available\r\n- UI breaks when user properties are undefined\r\n- Poor user experience during loading states\r\n- Potential crashes when image loading fails\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\nAdded robust error handling and graceful fallbacks:\r\n1. Implemented loading skeleton UI for initial state\r\n2. Added safe property access with optional chaining\r\n3. Included fallback values for missing user data\r\n4. Added image error handling\r\n5. Enhanced online status checking logic\r\n\r\n## Changes\r\n- Added loading skeleton UI with animation\r\n- Implemented null check for selectedUser\r\n- Added optional chaining (?.) for accessing user properties\r\n- Added fallback values:\r\n  - \"Unknown User\" for missing fullName\r\n  - \"/avatar.png\" for missing profilePic\r\n  - \"User\" for missing image alt text\r\n- Added onError handler for image loading failures\r\n- Made online status check more robust\r\n",
