        "body": "\r\n\r\nDescription:\r\n## Problem\r\nThe chat container was attaching a scroll reference to every message in the conversation, causing potential performance issues and inconsistent auto-scrolling behavior.\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\n- Modified the message rendering logic to attach the `messageEndRef` only to the last message in the chat\r\n- Added index tracking in the messages map function to identify the last message\r\n- Optimized the scroll behavior by using conditional ref assignment\r\n\r\n## Changes\r\n- Updated `ChatContainer.jsx` to use `index === messages.length - 1` condition for ref assignment\r\n- Improved code efficiency by removing unnecessary ref assignments\r\n",
