        "body": "\n## Description\nThe Projects component currently has inconsistencies in how project types are named and filtered, which affects the component's functionality and maintainability.\n\n### Current Behavior\n- Project types are inconsistently named:\n  - Using \"current\" and \"current1\" for ongoing projects\n  - Using \"upcoming\" instead of \"future\"\n  - Filter buttons use different names than actual project types\n- This causes:\n  - Some projects not showing up in correct filters\n  - Confusing code maintenance\n  - Potential bugs in filtering logic\n\n### Expected Behavior\n- Consistent naming across all project types:\n  - \"ongoing\" for current projects\n  - \"future\" for upcoming projects\n  - \"past\" for past projects\n- Filter buttons should match exactly with project types\n- Clear and maintainable filtering logic\n\n\n\n",
